transcript:
Agent: Assalam o Alaikum, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL
Customer: 이해가 되질 않네
Agent: Assalam o Alaikum, mein Ahmed
Customer: 끝!
Agent: Wa Alaikum Assalam, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL se. Aap ki madad kese kar sakta hoon?
Customer: Hello, Sir, you're on.
Customer: حمد مجھے اپنی بیلنس انکوائری کرنی ہے
Agent: Zaroor, ab aap apna TPIN batayein, jo ke chaar alag digits par mushtamil ho.
Agent: Shukriya. Ab barah-e-karam apna account number verification ke liye batayein.
Agent: Shukriya. Verification ke liye ab apna account number batayein.
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 50,000 rupees hai.
Customer: shhh
Agent: Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
